These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: salsa, metal, jazz, electronic, r&b, soul, gospel
1. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
4. the fan of r&b is between the fan of salsa and the fan of jazz##2
5. the fan of electronic is between the fan of metal and the fan of salsa##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | jazz | r&b | salsa | electronic | metal | soul |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: sudoku, photography, rock-climbing, reading, hiking, card-games, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Hobby   | card-games | woodworking | sudoku | rock-climbing | reading | photography | hiking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, skydiving, singing, cooking, dancing, collecting, board-games
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Hobby   | board-games | collecting | dancing | skydiving | camping | singing | cooking |

